-- в”Ђв”Ђ Arcads в”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђ
UPDATE tools SET
  short_description = COALESCE($q$Arcads is an AI video ad generator that turns text scripts into realistic UGC-style video ads using a library of over 1,000 AI actors.$q$, short_description),
  pricing_model = COALESCE($q$subscription$q$, pricing_model),
  starting_price = COALESCE($q$$110/month$q$, starting_price),
  founded_year = COALESCE(2024, founded_year),
  company_size = COALESCE(NULL, company_size),
  headquarters = COALESCE($q$Mont-Saint-Aignan, France$q$, headquarters),
  languages = ARRAY[$q$English$q$]::text[],
  seo_title = COALESCE($q$Arcads Review 2026: AI Video Ad Generator Pricing$q$, seo_title),
  seo_meta_description = COALESCE($q$Arcads turns scripts into UGC-style video ads with 1,000+ AI actors. See 2026 pricing, features, pros and cons for this AI ad creation platform.$q$, seo_meta_description),
  llm_readable_summary = COALESCE($q$Arcads is an AI-powered video advertising platform built by the French company FRESHR SAS, founded in 2024 by Romain Torres and Dylan Fournier. The product lets marketers turn a plain text script into a finished, realistic video ad in a few minutes by selecting from a library of more than 1,000 AI-generated actors, or by creating a custom AI avatar. Beyond the core actor-driven video generation, Arcads offers AI video editing tools including automatic subtitles, video upscaling, video extension, emotion control for the AI actors, and translation and voiceover localization into more than 30 languages, which lets a single script be turned into ad variants for multiple international markets. The platform also includes a workflow canvas that lets marketing teams collaborate on creating, testing, and scaling ad variations together, along with a library of pre-built ad templates optimized for direct-response and performance marketing formats such as UGC-style testimonials and product demos. Arcads is aimed at direct-to-consumer brands, mobile app studios, marketing and creative agencies, e-commerce companies, SaaS businesses, and lead-generation advertisers who need to produce large volumes of testable ad creative quickly and cheaply compared to traditional video production or influencer/UGC creator sourcing. The company has stated that ads made with its tools have generated over one billion views in aggregate. Commercially, Arcads runs on a subscription and credit model rather than a free tier: the Starter plan is priced at roughly $110 per month for 10 video credits (about $11 per finished video), while a Creator plan doubles output to 20 videos per month at the same per-video rate; credits reset monthly and do not roll over, and there is no free trial. In December 2025 Arcads raised a $16 million seed round with participation from Eurazeo, Alpha Intelligence Capital, and Sequoia's Scout program, underscoring investor interest in AI-generated performance advertising. Arcads competes with other AI UGC ad generators and text-to-video ad tools; its main differentiators are the scale of its AI actor library, built-in multilingual localization, and a workflow designed specifically for iterative performance-marketing testing rather than general-purpose video creation.$q$, llm_readable_summary),
  status = 'published',
  noindex = false,
  sitemap_eligible = true,
  published_at = COALESCE(published_at, now()),
  updated_at = now()
WHERE id = '1635aea1-58d7-4783-be12-99aed0d3646f';

